{{{1
配置 
让pixel 完整输出日志
persist.logd.size=256m
persist.logd.kernel.size=256m
stop logd && start logd
kernel.msgmnb = 1073741824  # 1GB
kernel.msgmax = 524288      # 单条消息最大长度
logcat -G 256m
echom "7 4 1 7" > /proc/sys/kernel/printk  所有内核日志都输出
echo 256000000 > /sys/module/logger/parameters/log_size
nohup logcat -b all -v threadtime -f /sdcard/bluetooth_debug.log >/dev/null 2>&1 &
/system/etc/init/hw/init.usb.rc  设置adb 端口5555 setprop service.adb.tcp.port 5555

开机自动抓日志

system/etc/init/hw/init.rc 有如下几个步骤
1.early-init → 2. init → 3. early-fs → 4. fs → 5. post-fs → 6. early-boot → 7. boot → 8. 按 class 启动服务
在post-fs 阶段logd （log 守护进程） 被拉起来，此时会通过logcatd 这个服务去抓取log 放到/data/misc/logd 目录

system/etc/init/logcatd.rc  logcatd 服务
service logcatd /system/bin/logcatd -L -b all -v threadtime -v usec -v printable -D -f /data/misc/logd/main_log -r ${logd.logpersistd.rotate_kbytes:-32720} -n 10 -G 256m  --id=${ro.build.id}
    class late_start
    disabled
    # logd for write to /data/misc/logd, log group for read from log daemon
    user logd
    group log
    task_profiles ServiceCapacityLow
    oom_score_adjust -600

